  "title": "Bind SkPictureShader",
  "body": "**Description of changes**\r\n\r\nAllow create shaders from SKPicture\r\n\r\n- Related to issue #969 \r\n\r\n**API Changes**\r\n\r\nAdded: \r\n \r\n- \u0060sk_shader_t SkiaApi.sk_shader_new_picture(sk_picture_t src, SKShaderTileMode tmx, SKShaderTileMode tmy, ref SKMatrix matrix, ref SKRect tile)\u0060\r\n- \u0060SKShader SKShader.CreatePicture (SKPicture src, SKShaderTileMode tmx, SKShaderTileMode tmy, SKMatrix localMatrix, SKRect tile)\u0060\r\n- \u0027SKShaderTest.CanDrawWithCreatePictureShader()\u0027\r\n\r\n**Behavioral Changes**\r\n\r\nAs mentioned in [issue](https://github.com/mono/SkiaSharp/issues/969#issuecomment-535925348): existing native libraries already support this changes!\r\n\r\n**PR Checklist**\r\n\r\n- [x] Has tests\r\n- [x] Rebased on top of master at time of PR\r\n- [ ] Changes adhere to coding standard\r\n- [ ] Updated documentation\r\n",
